[A]LEVFORCE [level][-] [command]
[A]If a '-' is ommitted from the end of the level, forces all players at
[A]the level given and above. If the '-' is given, forces all players at
[A]the level given and below. Note that is a higher player has on NoForce
[A]that they won't be forced.
[A]
[A]  Examples: levforce 3000 shout Coolness!
[A]            levforce 12- jump
[A]^
