[PWeather]WEATHER [type]
[PWeather]Changes the weather to a specified type. The types are:
[PWeather]
[PWeather]    CLEAR     : Make the weather nice and clear.
[PWeather]    RAIN      : Make it rain.
[PWeather]    SHOWERS   : Make it shower.
[PWeather]    HAILING   : Make it hail.
[PWeather]    SNOW      : Make it snow.
[PWeather]    DRIZZLE   : Make it drizzle.
[PWeather]    STORMY    : Make it stormy.
[PWeather]    BLIZZARD  : Make it blizzard.
[PWeather]^
